  <h3>Share something <em>only you</em> could tell us about this line.</h3>
  <p>For example:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>A behind the scenes story or a personal anecdote</li>
    <li>Set the record straight about an ambiguous or misunderstood reference</li>
  </ul>
  <h4>Style Help</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <p>Add an image, video, or tweet by pasting in the URL:</p>
      <pre>http://genius.com/logo.png</pre>
    </li>
    <li><p>Add a link like this:</p>
      <pre>
  [Check out my fave website](http://genius.com)</pre>
      <p></p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <em>
  <a href='#' class='formatting_help_toggle'>
